  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Ghoul.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong data-start=\"64\" data-end=\"77\">Category:</strong> Clan<br data-start=\"82\" data-end=\"85\" /><strong data-start=\"85\" data-end=\"102\">Prerequisite:</strong> Ghoul Clan<br data-start=\"113\" data-end=\"116\" />Your hunger knows no bounds. You have even started to satiate yourself in the midst of combat, refreshing lost RC Cells. You gain the following benefits:<br data-start=\"269\" data-end=\"272\" />• When you would make a bite attack, you can choose to forgo adding your ability modifier to the damage to instead force the target to make a Constitution saving throw against your Taijutsu save DC, gaining 1 rank of bleed on a failure.<br data-start=\"508\" data-end=\"511\" />• You gain an additional number of RC Cells equal to half your level (Rounded Up).<br data-start=\"593\" data-end=\"596\" />• When you would use an action to consume a corpse, you instead gain an increased number of RC Cells from the corpse. (Minion: 2, Standard: 5, Elite: 7, Solo: 15).</p>",
